replyContent: It looks like you scanned a barcode that even Google doesn't know about. For best results, please scan a standard UPC-A or EAN-13 code with either 12 or 13 digits. If it is a common product which is also sold online, you'll for sure get results. If Amazon or eBay offer the product,  you'll even see the price directly in the app.
